data.description: DUAL OWNERS SUITE is a plus in this open Magnolia floorplan ESTATES SERIES in Frisco Lakes, 55+ Active Adult Community with Exceptional Resort Style Living. The Sunroom is now used a Formal Dining room but can be a card, game room, craft room, enough room for a pool table. The upgraded Chef’s Kitchen has 42-inch cabinets, pendant lights, breakfast nook overlooks a large living area. Additional shelving added in pantry, Master closets. Study with French Doors large enough for office furniture. Tray Ceiling with Crown molding, 5-inch baseboards with wood flooring. Master Bath has extra upgraded built-in cabinets for more storage galore. The lovely backyard is fully fenced with gates on each side. Three Amenity Centers, each with outdoor resort style pools, fitness center includes the very popular Pickleball plus Bocce Ball, Tennis, indoor, outdoor pools, billiards & so much more. This 55+ Community offers a fun and involved Lifestyle that you don’t want to miss at this time of your life!
